This is my first deathrun map, it's kinda simple in terms of detail but all the traps and everything else works just fine as far as I know.

Features:

• 16 Traps - 14 Controlled by the TR's, 1 Random, 1 Skill.

• 3 Endings - Bhop, Knife, Spawn.

• 4 Secrets - 10 Special smoke grenades.

• Some parts of the floor break when touched.

• Anti-AFK

• 56 Spawn Points - 54 CT's and 2 TR's.

• Trap's button, when pressed, is locked and has a delay of 25 seconds until it can be pressed again.


I also included a text file with the secrets location in the .RAR file, just extract it and open in the notepad. 

If there are any bugs, please report them and I'll fix as soon as possible.

Thanks!

Deathrun Steam Works is basicaly seventh sense, except it looks a whole lot better, it has been made fairer, all the bugs (that i know of) have been fixed and better sounds have been added.

Deathrun Steam Works is a very balanced map, good for all skills of death runners. The map has 155 spawn points (no idea why I didn’t stop at 64). It is based in an abstract metal tunnelling system with a lot of wood.

Here are the traps in the DeathRun:

1. Reverse break floor
2. Fire platform
3. Double crusher arms
4. Fan hall
5. Deadly steam jets
6. Floor drop
7. Electric wire
8. Giant hammer
9. Floor smackers
10. Gear grinder
11. Flying barrels
12. Spinning floor thingys
13. Laser crusher
14. Exploding barrel jump (no terrorist)
15. Spinning gear, wall trap
16. Good ol’ crusher

The Mini-Games at the end of my map include:

1. Deadly saw blade cannon knife arena
2. Easy bunny hop
3. Duck shootout, fairground style!

The map also includes:

1. A giant 7
2. A spiral grenade
3. A smoke grenade
4. And a secret ending

The map also has all the Anti-AFK feature needed to keep the game running smoothly which means that an admin doesn’t always have to be present to stop those annoying AFK people.

Hi!

This map has been on i3D's Deathrun server for some time now (84.244.187.239:27015), and it's been a big hit. So I'm uploading it on FPSbanana for all the other servers. It's best played on servers with 32+ slots, but a max of 64.

It's quite a random map, no theme intended, just fun!

v1 updates:

- Fixed major lag issue,
- Fixed sound bugs,
- CT's can now run faster with their weapons,
- Trap times reduced,
- a few other little things.

Hope you all like it, have fun.

After 2 years I fixed this map. For me this map is a failure, but some people like it, I fixed map for them. I'm not going to edit/update this map anymore!


Credits

Filo (a.k.a. Fighter) - map creator

Models - I don't know who made them, I found them on other site.

Glaber - E-123 Omega Model

phqnix - textures


Special thanks:

Berklej and Carlos Olivera  - thanks for testing map

Metz10 - thanks for help with adding content to .BSP


E-mail: defenderpl@gazeta.pl

***CHANGES MADE TO V3***
- Trap nr 1 changed.
- Spawn rate of the barrels in the second trap reduced and will no longer cause severe fps lagg to people without super computers.
- Map optimized more.
- Added damage filter for FALL damage only
- Song nade removed.
- Another sprite trail nade added.
- The last "event" before the map is completed by the CT's have been COMPLETELY revamped - much, much easier.
- The BHOP ending have been completely revamped too, and multi jumps on platform have been added for the deathrun servers without a easy bhop plugin (also i've tested the bhop with the absolute worst settings, it is very possible to complete!)
- Some textures changed.
- This map is no longer in beta, this is the third release and there is no game breaking bugs, no excessive lag creating areas, no broken traps, no unintended stuff pretty much!
I hope you enjoy, feedback is always welcome!

************************************************************************
